room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Every Second Counts ESC in Beaufort (SC)
room_description:
Area 51 and Roswell N.M. has been the focal point of alien conspiracy theories in America for decades. Intense secrecy surrounding the base and highly guarded to present day. Many believe alien spacecraft crash-landed 70 years ago.
Is the military still covering up the truth about dead bodies of aliens found? While witness claim to have seen flying saucers and unusual debris. What exactly has gone on inside of Area 51? Bring your friends and discover the retrieval and cover-up of Extraterrestrial Life inside Area 51!
